{"tid":251771,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【今日最慘烈】首都廣場慘蝕82%拍賣 開價55萬","createTime":"2017-05-21T08:15:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T01:58:50.000Z","uid":17738,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"789137c4a532dd745339b7941c7e8e92ba3d259b","tid":251771,"uid":17738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T08:15:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170521/large/1495351772_1567.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170521%2Flarge%2F1495351772_1567.jpg&h=15265c1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屬經典死場的尖沙嘴首都廣場再有劏舖勁蝕放售。環亞物業網頁顯示，位於首都廣場3樓一個單號舖位，將於本月23日（周二）拍賣，開價僅55萬元。土地註冊處資料顯示，業主於2013年1月以307.8萬元買入該舖位，當時「3球」現金買舖，沒有承造按揭，四年後踏上「死場」之路，不惜勁蝕82%的開價求售，若成功以此價售出，將慘蝕252.8萬元，樓價四年間跌剩不足兩成。<br />\n<br />\n首都廣場過去已錄得最少7宗蝕讓，蝕讓幅度介乎56%至85%。其中3樓雙號舖，投資者2013年以331.5萬元買入，今年3月以50萬元賣出，勁蝕85%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56722604&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170521\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56722604%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170521&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=e123a49a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56722604%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170521&h=d72806c3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56722604&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170521</a>"},{"pid":"37c93ac66e5bb0ae4caafafa9121cc274d7e0071","tid":251771,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:02:20.000Z","msg":"慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c7e415f6a2648e8bf07ebd7bc0657796f4ba8a","tid":251771,"uid":44486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim